<p>amstar2Vis: An R package for presenting the critical appraisal of systematic reviews based on the items of AMSTAR 2. <strong>Konstantinos I. Bougioukas</strong>, Paschalis Karakasis, Konstantinos Pamporis, Emmanouil Bouras, Anna-Bettina Haidich <em>Research Synthesis Methods</em> (2024)<br>
